The paper focuses on Machine Comprehension (MC) task in Natural Language Processing (NLP) field, which involves techniques such as attention mechanism, memory network, and lexical understanding. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related tasks. The paper also involves machine learning techniques such as gating mechanism and checking layer, which are commonly used in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Learning). The paper also involves neural networks, which are commonly used in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval techniques, which are commonly used in cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
